Objectives
Become more comfortable with Python.
Gain experience with Flask.
Learn to use SQL to interact with databases.
Overview
In this project, there is a book review website where Users will be able to register for the website and then log in using their username and password.
Once they log in, they will be able to search for books, leave reviews for individual books, and see the reviews made by other people.
